{"tid":1556323,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"英國國會聯署 - 要求英國收回香港","createTime":"2019-09-09T16:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T18:09:25.000Z","uid":271280,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3fc9c20f4fa510562c953fd0d1a402d58673c17f","tid":1556323,"uid":271280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"我曾經去英國國會申請petition, 要求英國收回香港, 收到以下回覆, <br />\n我覺得重點在於:<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> a decision for the people of Hong Kong</span></span> (香港人的決定)。<br />\n我會盡快再整一個聯署(非英國/白宮的), 個停止日期我會set到9月30日<br />\n如果足夠的聯署 (最少50萬人),之後我會再去英國國會petition。<br />\n我會在意一定要去英國國會聯署 係因為人數夠10萬人就可以上國會討論<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係時候大家好好想想地希望人地點具體幫我地。</span><br />\n<br />\n比啲意見我, 應該在甚麼平台發起聯署。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n信件內容:<br />\nWe rejected your petition &ldquo;Request The United Kingdom to reinstate jurisdiction of Hong Kong&rdquo;<br />\nPetitions: UK Government and Parliament <br />\n <br />\nWe rejected the petition you created &ndash; &ldquo;Request The United Kingdom to reinstate jurisdiction of Hong Kong&rdquo;.<br />\n<br />\nIt&rsquo;s about something that the UK Government or Parliament is not responsible for.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">This would be a decision for the people of Hong Kong.</span></span><br />\n<br />\nClick this link to see your rejected petition:<br />\nView your rejected petition<br />\n<br />\nWe only reject petitions that don&rsquo;t meet the petition standards:<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/help#standards\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fhelp%23standards&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNlYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=bf8ccea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/help#standards</a><br />\n<br />\nIf you want to try again, click here to start a petition:<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/check\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2Fcheck&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNlYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=e3d8ff6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/check</a><br />\n<br />\nThanks,<br />\nThe Petitions team<br />\nUK Government and Parliament"},{"pid":"8ae82407ba96777beecc2da416f99504249b2f1e","tid":1556323,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:31:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"148c72cf02184f579258784529840f144a67aa01","tid":1556323,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:32:27.000Z","msg":"叫埋美國介入，先叫英國扲返香港，再叫美國比錢租/買香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa6170684a7876fee3428a6568e96f847ea1182","tid":1556323,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:33:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3c1c60639fc7b77af29528a0826d54f8eeb57a5","tid":1556323,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"148c72cf02184f579258784529840f144a67aa01","tid":1556323,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:32:27.000Z","msg":"叫埋美國介入，先叫英國扲返香港，再叫美國比錢租/買香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:35:25.000Z","msg":"推呢個"},{"pid":"063c8cf258a637b2cf83cd40075ff1c28e86a27f","tid":1556323,"uid":271280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"148c72cf02184f579258784529840f144a67aa01","tid":1556323,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:32:27.000Z","msg":"叫埋美國介入，先叫英國扲返香港，再叫美國比錢租/買香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:35:48.000Z","msg":"係可以拉美國落水, 要佢做公証人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">問題係我應該在甚麼平台發起聯署??</span>"},{"pid":"2d5c25582b770efb4df8ac292993db6e4ddd22b4","tid":1556323,"uid":111996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"